extends layout

block content
  .navbar.navbar-inverse.navbar-fixed-top
    .navbar-inner
      .container
        a.btn.btn-navbar(data-toggle='collapse', data-target='.nav-collapse')
          span.icon-bar
          span.icon-bar
          span.icon-bar
        a.brand(href='#') The quest game
        .nav-collapse.collapse
          ul.nav
            li.active
              a(href='/game') Game
            li
              a(href='/user/login') Login
            li
              a(href='user/register') Register
        //
          /.nav-collapse 
  .container
    //
       Main message
    .hero-unit
      h1= title
      p
        | Meet the new very addictive, _open source_ 
        | , realtime MMO game. The goal is simple - steal the treasure. Have fun NOW with your friends or other players all over the world.
      p
        a.btn.btn-primary.btn-large(href='/game') Play now » 
        span.visitorsTitle  Visitors:
        span.visitorsCount= 0

        script.
          var socket = io.connect();
          socket.on('visitorsOnline', function (data) {
            $(".visitorsCount").html(data);
          });
    // columns 

    .row
      .span4
        h2 How the game was born
        p
          | Once upon a time there were a group of hackers who wanted to teach how to code on node.js. The same time Varna Lab announced the upcomming event - free node.js course. The magic was born.
        p
          a.btn(href='http://www.varnalab.org/') Varna Lab Hackerspace »
      .span4
        h2 Who created the game
        p
          | The inisial game was developed with much love for 4-5 hours from the course head man 
          a(href='https://github.com/outbounder') outbounder. 
          Then almost all of course participants started with pull requests from 
          a(href='https://github.com/outbounder/node-thequest/graphs/contributors') contributors.
          | To see list of all contributors and game code click this button
        p
          a.btn(href='https://github.com/outbounder/node-thequest/graphs/contributors') Contributors »
      .span4
        h2 I wanna contribute
        p
          | If you want to add your super feature to the game, do not hesitate to make a pull request. All kind of help (code, design, servers, mentioning, feedback) is highly appreciated.
        p
          a.btn(href='https://trello.com/board/the-quest/508c26ce9334dadb7000298d') Leave us feedback »
    hr
    footer
      p © VarnaLab.org 2012